channel.title: Sigh, another project I guess
channel.description:
Well, Dimmu didn't turn out so good, because people stopped posting. I decided to start a new project based on PimpScape (Yes I know, "pmg pimpscape is lyk for lozerz lelelele!")
I don't know what I'll be naming it, so lets go with Projekt Nameless (Yes I know I spelled Project wrong, it's the whole point lols.)
What else.. I won't be making a site, because it'll end up not being used, because I'm still working on bits of Dimmu.
So, lets see...
Updates: Name changed Removed tons of shit Added in a couple custom methods for special reasons >.>
Future updates: More classes, smaller client Specials Few more skills for now Enhance PKing Better Magic Better Ranging Work on PKing again
That's probably it for now, nothing special, just another project that will fail, because I'm bored with Dimmu because of the LACK OF POSTS.
Sooooo... Thanks for reading, I'll update this daily probably, and might end up using this as a base for a server. Sincerely, Fr33b1e
